# Base UI library: your chosen UI library

## Package import
Always import from `test-client-design-system` — NEVER from the underlying library directly:
```tsx
import { Button, vars } from 'test-client-design-system';
import 'test-client-design-system/src/design-tokens/tokens.css';
```

## Design Token Rules
- NEVER hardcode hex colors — use CSS variables or `vars` references
- NEVER hardcode font sizes or spacing values
- TypeScript access: `import { designTokens, vars } from 'test-client-design-system'`

